      "name": "PIV velocity field comparison — FDA pump operating point A",
      "description": "Comparison of CFD-predicted velocity magnitude contours against particle image velocimetry (PIV) measurements at the primary operating point (5 L/min, 3500 RPM). Normalized RMS error across the measurement plane is 6.3 %, within the 8 % acceptance criterion. This result was produced by the structured validation campaign documented in Activity act:morrison-piv-campaign-2024Q1.",
