      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Pump pressure-head curve validation across speed range",
      "description": "Predicted hydraulic pressure head (ΔP) versus flow-rate curves compared against benchtop measurements at three rotational speeds. Mean absolute error across all measurement points is 4.1 mmHg, satisfying the 6 mmHg acceptance criterion.",
